<!-- PROBLEM -->
<section id="problem">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-label">Sound familiar?</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">You don't need more apps.<br>You need less noise.</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">If any of these feel like your everyday, you're not broken — you just need a simpler system.</p>
    <div class="problem-grid">
      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="problem-icon">😵</div>
        <h3>Overwhelmed</h3>
        <p>Your to-do list never ends. Every morning starts with dread instead of direction.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="problem-icon">⏳</div>
        <h3>Procrastinating</h3>
        <p>You know what needs to get done — but you keep putting it off until tomorrow.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="problem-icon">📋</div>
