      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SOLUTION -->
<section id="solution">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-label">The System</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Less thinking.<br>More doing.</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">The Lazy Panda system strips productivity down to what actually works. No 12-week challenges. No complicated frameworks.</p>
    <div class="solution-steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div class="step-text">
          <h3>Choose 3–5 tasks per day</h3>
          <p>Not 20. Not 50. Pick the three tasks that actually matter. That's your whole list. Everything else waits.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div class="step-text">
          <h3>Follow the simple daily structure</h3>
          <p>Morning intention → focused work blocks → short reset. Repeatable, friction-free, and done in minutes to set up.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div class="step-text">
          <h3>Spend less time planning</h3>
          <p>The system does the thinking so you don't have to. Open your planner, follow the structure, and move.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">4</div>
